Several thousand protestors are gathered in Shibuya, Tokyo for an [anti-
nuclear power demonstration](http://57nonukes.tumblr.com/). This demo follows
another held on [April 10th](http://410nonuke.tumblr.com/)
([video](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uPN2kJn2WgE)). Hiruma Takashi posted
photos of [arrests](https://picasaweb.google.com/106470437217907126638/57#).
Twitter users are using the hashtag is
[#57nonukes](http://twitter.com/#!/search/%2357nonukes).

